          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>One may notice that the <fr:link type="local" href="work-0001.xml" addr="work-0001" title="Judgement Calculi">judgement calculus</fr:link> is merely a fragment of FOL. It amounts to a syntactic change.
  <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[     \mathcal {J} := R(\overline {e}) \,\, | \,\, \forall  \, x. \,\, \mathcal {J} \,\, | \,\, \mathcal {J} \Rightarrow  \mathcal {J}   ]]></fr:tex></fr:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
          <fr:backmatter />
        </fr:tree>
